🧠 Now comes the key point

Since your cluster is DOWN, IDMS is NOT applied yet

So node only uses:

/etc/containers/registries.conf


---

✅ Fix NOW (temporary recovery fix)

Edit on SNO node:

vi /etc/containers/registries.conf

Update to:

[[registry]]
prefix = ""
location = "quay.io/openshift-release-dev"
mirror-by-digest-only = true

[[registry.mirror]]
location = "bastion-sno.lab.ocp.lan:8443/ocp4/openshift4/openshift-release-dev"


